    dc:description "Figs 1–22. General appearance of Afroceto gen. n. species: A. martini (Simon, 1897) comb. n. female (1) and male (2); A. arca sp. n. female (3) and male (4); A. bulla sp. n. female (5); A. bisulca male (6); A. capensis sp. n. female (7) and male (8); A. coenosa (Simon, 1897) comb. n. female (9); A. corcula sp. n. female (10); A. croeseri sp. n. female (11) and male (12); A. flabella sp. n. male (13) and female (14); A. gracilis sp. n. male (15); A. plana sp. n. male (16) and female (17); A. porrecta sp. n. male (18); A. rotunda sp. n. male (19) and female (20); A. spicula sp. n. male (21) and female (22)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7913563/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7913599>
    dc:description "Figs68–71.Afroceto croeseri sp.n.female (68) and male(69–71):(68) epigyne,ventral view; (69)schematic representation of cusp arrangement on legs I and II; (70) left palp, ventral view; (71) left palp, retrolateral view. Scale bars (68, 70, 71) = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7913599/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

